            <pb facs="#f0001" />
            <head>AMERICAN STATISTICS. </head>
            <p>The following details have been furnished by<lb/>M. Humboldt respecting America, and
                are con-<lb/>sidered accurate:&#x2014; </p>
            <table>
                <row>
                    <cell></cell>
                    <cell>
                        Sq. leagues
                    </cell>
                    <cell>Inhabitants in 1823. </cell>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <cell>United States contain </cell>
                    <cell>
                        174,300
                    </cell>
